      "title": "Project Core: Interactive Portfolio",
      "subtext": "An immersive, space-themed portfolio built from the ground up with vanilla JavaScript.",
      "color": "hsl(45, 100%, 75%)",
      "body": "This portfolio is a testament to the power of foundational web technologies. The entire experience, from the procedurally generated galaxy to the cinematic transitions and interactive solar systems, is rendered on the HTML5 Canvas. The architecture is built around a robust, state-driven application controller that manages different views and transitions seamlessly."
